text: Agata Guściora (born 6 October 1994) is a Polish footballer who plays as a defender and has appeared for the Poland women's national team. ==Career== Guściora has been capped for the Poland national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Polish women's footballers Category:Poland women's international footballers Category:Women's association football defenders
